 Apartment in late 2019. He\'s talented, self-critical, and struggling to finish his first full-length play. He had developed feel ... (109 more chars omitted)\\nPosition: Chez Lulu (French-American Bistro)/Bartender / Playwright (work), weekly income: 320, Tends bar four nights a week at Chez Lulu, earning tips and hourly wages. Writes in the mornings. Occasionally earns small fees from staged readings o ... (69 more chars omitted)","name":"read_scratchpad","role":"tool"}],"model":"my-vllm-model","tool_choice":"auto"}}')
